ize: xx-large;\">警告堅持要返工返學嘅人，即將面對惡犬強姦殺人滅口嘅危險，在網上廣傳！</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/nbQFJcX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/nbQFJcX</a><br />\n#131 回覆"},{"pid":"fa4e6d3d2b38a348d2c4aad48e5dafe5f5452afc","tid":1711163,"uid":98431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:29:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">【城大即時】1810 儘管學生宿舍處澄清警方七時半清場消息只是傳聞，不少外藉宿生仍選擇收拾包袱離開宿舍。<br />\n<br />\n城大小心 對家出鬼計引人走 可能想盡早清場</span>"},{"pid":"e4346f631a654920277ba0679efb935d116c1fd2","tid":1711163,"uid":4574,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:32:05.000Z","msg":"sorry 只會用call4van <br />\ntoo late too little"},{"pid":"a3a90063a90774450a2ed00bdeeb2c0c460c7592","tid":1711163,"uid":111448,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:33:02.000Z","msg":"nice job popo, 又搞到一間公司同你割蓆。都係果句，你肯轉過黎黃尼邊，香港人就會識做<br />\n<br />\n只要整大尼個黃色經濟圈，我地就更加有抗爭成本"},{"pid":"ce765d1799a8d221e238e005ad2e854b2123afac","tid":1711163,"uid":111448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3a90063a90774450a2ed00bdeeb2c0c460c7592","tid":1711163,"uid":111448,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:33:02.000Z","msg":"nice job popo, 又搞到一間公司同你割蓆。都係果句，你肯轉過黎黃尼邊，香港人就會識做<br />\n<br />\n只要整大尼個黃色經濟圈，我地就更加有抗爭成本"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:37:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">nice job popo, 又搞到一間公司同你割蓆。都係果句，你肯轉過黎黃<span style=\"color: red;\">呢</span>邊，香港人就會識做<br />\n只要整大<span style=\"color: red;\">呢</span>個黃色經濟圈，我地就更加有抗爭成本<br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"61046fe025c6631de1c9738709b019870d1b2f35","tid":1711163,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:39:33.000Z","msg":"連私人商標都拎就用黎"},{"pid":"6dc53c180d71def00aabc6aa47b655cbd4be8a1d","tid":1711163,"uid":307913,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"f3fc32d52a304a85ce4c688693369b8936a2fd6d","tid":1